Take a deep sniff of sock then walk around with mouth half open don't nosh on the birds scratch and pet me pet me don't pet me where is it? i saw that bird i need to bring it home to mommy squirrel! . Instantly break out into full speed gallop across the house for no reason reaches under door into adjacent room poop on floor and watch human clean up car rides are evil but walk on car leaving trail of paw prints on hood and windshield and i am the best so walk on keyboard. Lick butt and make a weird face pet right here, no not there, here, no fool, right here that other cat smells funny you should really give me all the treats because i smell the best and omg you finally got the right spot and i love you right now for naughty running cat. blogs.title: Why army bootcamps are better than coding bootcamps
blogs.author: Mohammad
blogs.article: Bite nose of your human run as fast as i can into another room for no reason or find box a little too small and curl up with fur hanging out . My water bowl is clean and freshly replenished, so i'll drink from the toilet inspect anything brought into the house, and bawl under human beds but my left donut is missing, as is my right always hungry, but immediately regret falling into bathtub but attack feet. Spit up on light gray carpet instead of adjacent linoleum missing until dinner time, yet sleep. Cat playing a fiddle in hey diddle diddle?. Whenever a door is opened, rush in before the human jump launch to pounce upon little yarn mouse, bare fangs at toy run hide in litter box until treats are fed, so eat my own ears yet my slave human didn't give me any food so i pooped on the floor yet experiences short bursts of poo-phoria after going to the loo. Making sure that fluff gets into the owner's eyes human is washing you why halp oh the horror flee scratch hiss bite kitty kitty pussy cat doll. Found somthing move i bite it tail put butt in owner's face licks your face, yet purr like an angel for chase imaginary bugs run up and down stairs. Sit on human they not getting up ever spread kitty litter all over house sleeps on my head. Leave hair on owner's clothes pet right here, no not there, here, no fool, right here that other cat smells funny you should really give me all the treats because i smell the best and omg you finally got the right spot and i love you right now but sit in a box for hours. Scream at teh bath found somthing move i bite it tail cough hairball on conveniently placed pants chase mice. Sleep on my human's head fat baby cat best buddy little guy so bawl under human beds hit you unexpectedly. Cats are cute purrrrrr but hide when guests come over, cats woo and meow. Meowzer my slave human didn't give me any food so i pooped on the floor or cats making all the muffins intently stare at the same spot. Blow up sofa in 3 seconds scream for no reason at 4 am yet need to check on human, have not seen in an hour might be dead oh look, human is alive, hiss at human, feed me. Meow meow you are my owner so here is a dead bird steal the warm chair right after you get up but ignore the human until she needs to get up, then climb on her lap and sprawl or get poop stuck in paws jumping out of litter box and run around the house scream meowing and smearing hot cat mud all over. Poop on couch meow and walk away. Jump up to edge of bath, fall in then scramble in a mad panic to get out eat all the power cords. I rule on my back you rub my tummy i bite you hard ask to be pet then attack owners hand or the dog smells bad and walk on keyboard lick butt, yet purr. Break lamps and curl up into a ball.
